description:
F*CK Corona and all the crazy bullshit that has to do with it! 🖕
.
I prefer a healthy lifestyle and don't have to be afraid of any viruses. 😜🌻
However, it makes me very sad to  see how many people are externally controlled and how politicians and the media are just playing with the peoples' fears... an invisible weapon with an incredibly great effect. 😔 SICK WORLD! 🤬
.
But I'm optimistic that this year could mean a change (also in people's minds)...
.
#staysafe my friends and #thinkpositive! 🤗😘🍀
.
